  "title": "A man spotted a white elongated UFO in Belo Horizonte-MG [1994]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/01/a-man-spotted-a-white-elongated-ufo-in-belo-horizonte-mg-1994/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1jM",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>DEC 3, 1994</strong>. Time: 14:14. Duration: 1 minute. In the neighborhood of Nova Lima, in Belo Horizonte, State of Minas Gerais, a person spotted an unidentified flying object of elongated shape and white color, flying at high speed. According to the witness, the UFO was small and was at a high altitude moving in the South-North direction of the city. The sighting took place with the naked eye, on an afternoon of clear sky and good visibility. There were no photographs or footage of the event.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.384. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Nova Lima, Minas Gerais”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
